<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.6">
<l>eḷki neñcē niṉaintiṅ kirunteṉ toḻutumeḻu</l>
<l>vaḷḷal māyaṉ maṇivaṇ ṇaṉemmāṉ maruvumiṭam</l>
<l>kaḷḷa viḻumma larkkā viyuntū maṭaṟkaitaiyum</l>
<l>puḷḷu maḷḷal paḻaṉaṅ kaḷumcūḻn tapullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, having sat here, thinking [of him], hesitating, what [then]?</l>
<l rend="indent">Arise; We will worship</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi surrounded by muddy, wet lands and birds,</l>
<l>Honeyed unfurled blossoming blue lilies, and white-leafed screw pine,</l>
<l>The place where lives our lord, the jewel-hued one, beneficent Māyaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
